do not add GREP_OPTIONS ... in .bashrc .
do not add GREP_OPTIONS ... in .exports

add the following alias items to .aliases

# Move export GREP_OPTIONS="--color=auto" (which is deprecated) from .exports to .alias
# Always enable colored `grep` output`
alias grep="grep --color=auto"
alias fgrep="fgrep --color=auto"
alias egrep="egrep --color=auto"


-> this must solve thie issue

grep: warning: GREP_OPTIONS is deprecated; please use an alias or script


